               java.lang.String username,
               java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String avatarUrl,
               java.lang.String serverUrl,
               java.lang.String accessToken)

        Created by Keval on 16/04/18.

        Parameters:
        userId - Unique id of the user on the CI server. For the same CI server, user id should be unique.
        username - Username on the CI server. For the same CI server, username should be unique.
        name - Full name of the user.
        avatarUrl - URL of the user's avatar image.
        serverUrl - Base url off the CI server. Using URL, application can identify which endpoint to call.
        accessToken - URL of the user's avatar image.
